title: Dakine Tanner Hall Team Fillmore Mitt
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Tanner Hall Team Fillmore Mitt.
Fillmore Features:
- Insert: Waterproof, windproof Polyurethane
- Insulation: High loft synthetic [ 60g / 170g ]
- Palm: Durable water repellent leather
- Shell: Nylon / Poly with DWR treatment
- Lining: 230g fleece
- Cuff Closure: Adjustable hook and loop
- Nose wipe thumb panels
